{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|2Ti|3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","chapter":3,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":1,"text":"But know this: Hard times will come in the last days.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":2,"text":"For people will be lovers of self, lovers of money, boastful, proud, demeaning, disobedient to parents, ungrateful, unholy,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":3,"text":"unloving, irreconcilable, slanderers, without self-control, brutal, without love for what is good,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":4,"text":"traitors, reckless, conceited, lovers of pleasure rather than lovers of God,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":5,"text":"holding to the form of godliness but denying its power. Avoid these people.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":6,"text":"For among them are those who worm their way into households and deceive gullible women overwhelmed by sins and led astray by a variety of passions,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":7,"text":"always learning and never able to come to a knowledge of the truth.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":8,"text":"Just as Jannes and Jambres resisted Moses, so these also resist the truth. They are men who are corrupt in mind and worthless in regard to the faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":9,"text":"But they will not make further progress, for their foolishness will be clear to all, as was the foolishness of Jannes and Jambres.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":10,"text":"But you have followed my teaching, conduct, purpose, faith, patience, love, and endurance,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":11,"text":"along with the persecutions and sufferings that came to me in Antioch, Iconium, and Lystra. What persecutions I endured —and yet the Lord rescued me from them all.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":12,"text":"In fact, all who want to live a godly life in Christ Jesus will be persecuted.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":13,"text":"Evil people and impostors will become worse, deceiving and being deceived.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":14,"text":"But as for you, continue in what you have learned and firmly believed. You know those who taught you,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":15,"text":"and you know that from infancy you have known the sacred Scriptures, which are able to give you wisdom for salvation through faith in Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":16,"text":"All Scripture is inspired by God and is profitable for teaching, for rebuking, for correcting, for training in righteousness,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":3,"verse":17,"text":"so that the man of God may be complete, equipped for every good work.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","chapter":3,"paragraphStarts":[1,6,10],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Difficult Times Ahead"},{"beforeVerse":10,"text":"Struggles in the Christian Life"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:3:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But know this: Hard times will come in the last days. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":39,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:6","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:5","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 3:3","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:18","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 6:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":39},{"label":"Php 1:6","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":6},{"label":"1Pt 1:5","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"2Pt 3:3","book":"2Pe","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"Jd 1:18